text: Anisophyllea penninervataVidal JE (1961) In: Bull. Soc. Bot. Fr. cviii. 72. is a tree species in the family Anisophylleaceae, with no subspecies listed in the Catalogue of Life. It has only been recorded from southern VietnamPlants of the World Online: Anisophyllea penninervata J.E.Vidal (retrieved 19 August 2019) where it may be called bất đẳng diệp. == References == == External Links== * Category:Anisophylleaceae Category:Flora of Indo-China Category:Trees of Vietnam
